{"tid":2203030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平：中方不接受人權“教師爺”，反對搞“雙重標準”","createTime":"2020-09-15T05:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:44:51.000Z","uid":137088,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2e134bb54133e6a6ce0dcd5a66707ea99d9724","tid":2203030,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:14:24.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平14日晚在北京同歐盟輪值主席國德國總理默克爾、歐洲理事會主席米歇爾、歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩共同舉行會晤，會晤以視頻方式舉行。<br />\n<br />\n  習近平強調，世界上沒有放之四海而皆準的人權發展道路，人權保障沒有最好，只有更好。各國首先應該做好自己的事情。相信歐方能夠解決好自身存在的人權問題。中方不接受人權&ldquo;教師爺&rdquo;，反對搞&ldquo;雙重標準&rdquo;。中方願同歐方本著相互尊重的原則加強交流，共同進步。"},{"pid":"b630aea0287bc69e835f45165384ed8106ef455a","tid":2203030,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6039832495eca4cc1fb5bc4231bd48d7d101e91","tid":2203030,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"最雙重標準咪中共"},{"pid":"3358417268546ed8e32fc5672e80514053e26515","tid":2203030,"uid":305358,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:18:05.000Z","msg":"咩人權&ldquo;教師爺&rdquo;，小學生亂Q咁作詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f85f2174d33f31ef4d7a7c20e2018eb78146d3","tid":2203030,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:19:24.000Z","msg":"我想要翻譯<br />\n睇唔l明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133cbecf8a3f5d9a58e1df18ed2066d8e655a123","tid":2203030,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"個文膽打稿打多左個關聯字唔記得刪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faaa099a6c189abdcf8f3b4921ca8f4db9b795a","tid":2203030,"uid":59328